author: @ortzg
text: Just wondering what other people's experience with quandl is like. I just tried to load the complete financial ratios of around 4 companies but the csv file i got back is only partially filled. I tried with 2 companies and it's the same thing. In both cases the csv returned exactly 102 columns (including the date column) that got filled. The rest of the remaining columns are empty It seems the 102 columns is a very limiting factor if one needs bigger dataset.
